ECHO ===== RELATIONS ENGINE (CURRENT BACKEND) =====
REL LIST
REL CLEAR ALL
REL ADD STUDENTS ENROLL ON SID
REL ADD ENROLL CLASSES ON CLS_ID
REL LIST
REL REFRESH
REL_LIST
REL_REFRESH
CMDREL
CMDREL LIST
CMDREL REFRESH

ECHO ===== RELATIONS ENGINE (FOXPRO NORMALIZATION CANARIES - EXPECT FAIL UNTIL WIRED) =====
SELECT STUDENTS
SET RELATION OFF ALL
SET RELATION TO SID INTO ENROLL
REL LIST

SELECT ENROLL
SET RELATION TO CLS_ID INTO CLASSES
REL LIST

SELECT ENROLL
SET RELATION OFF INTO CLASSES
REL LIST

SELECT STUDENTS
SET RELATION TO SID INTO ENROLL, SID INTO STUD_MAJ
REL LIST

SELECT STUDENTS
SET RELATION TO SID INTO ENROLL
SET RELATION ADDITIVE TO SID INTO STUD_MAJ
REL LIST